title: Pence To Speak At Delta High School "Energy Summit"

outline.text: Pence To Speak At Delta High School "Energy Summit"
U.S. Congressman Mike Pence will speak at Delta High School’s second "Energy Summit" on
Friday, September 10. The Congressman will speak to around 400 high school students about
11:30 AM – Congressman Pence to speak at Delta High School "Energy Summit"
